---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---

<section class="hero">
  <p class="hero-eyebrow">Spencer Pollock</p>
  <h1 class="hero-headline">
    Platform and developer<br />experience engineer.
  </h1>
  <p class="hero-subhead">
    I build the systems between <code>git push</code> and production — CI/CD
    pipelines, delivery infrastructure, and the tooling product teams ship
    with.
  </p>
  <p class="hero-supporting">
    Currently at Wolters Kluwer, where a custom delivery framework I designed
    cut customer deployment times by <strong>40%</strong>.
  </p>
  <p class="hero-location text-subtle">Based in North Vancouver, BC.</p>

  <ul class="hero-links">
    <li>
      <a href="mailto:spencer@spollock.ca">Email</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://github.com/srepollock" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        GitHub
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/srepollock" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        LinkedIn
      </a>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding-block: var(--space-24) var(--space-16);
    max-width: 52rem;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .hero-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-4xl), 6vw, var(--text-5xl));
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .hero-subhead {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 40rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .hero-subhead code {
    font-size: 0.88em;
    background: var(--color-code-bg);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
  }

  .hero-supporting {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 40rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .hero-supporting strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .hero-location {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .hero-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    list-style: none;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  .hero-links a {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transition:
      color var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out),
      border-color var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .hero-links a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>